data.text:
Rick Phillips, singer/songwriter on keyboard and vocals; originals and re-crafted covers. Come relax and enjoy an evening with us.

Our live music events are complimentary for Henry Earl wine club members; for all other patrons, there is a $15.00 minimum purchase required per person.

Our full menu will be available for your enjoyment.

We a non-alcoholic beverage menu which includes live music for those

who do not consume alcoholic beverages.

Our live music events are not suitable for children under 17 years old. Any person under 21 years of age must be accompanied by an adult.

Cheers!
